description: The Parcel 2012 feature contains tax parcel polygons for the 2012 property tax assessment at the County. This feature reflects tax parcel polygons as they existed from 1/1/2012 through 12/31/2012. Each parcel is uniquely identified with a Property Index Number (PIN).
